1 REM CrossBasic Always-On-Top Graphics Demo
2 REM This program demonstrates the always-on-top graphics window feature

10 REM Initialize graphics mode
20 GRAPHICS

30 REM Draw title area
40 COLOR 1
50 FOR I = 0 TO 800 STEP 20
60 FOR J = 0 TO 50 STEP 20
70 PLOT I, J
80 NEXT J
90 NEXT I

100 REM Draw colorful pattern
110 FOR ANGLE = 0 TO 360 STEP 10
120 COLOR (ANGLE / 40) + 1
130 X = 400 + 150 * COS(ANGLE * 3.14159 / 180)
140 Y = 300 + 150 * SIN(ANGLE * 3.14159 / 180)
150 CIRCLE X, Y, 20
160 NEXT ANGLE

170 REM Draw center design
180 COLOR 2
190 CIRCLE 400, 300, 100
200 COLOR 3
210 CIRCLE 400, 300, 75
220 COLOR 4
230 CIRCLE 400, 300, 50
240 COLOR 5
250 CIRCLE 400, 300, 25

260 REM Draw corner decorations
270 COLOR 6
280 CIRCLE 100, 100, 30
290 CIRCLE 700, 100, 30
300 CIRCLE 100, 500, 30
310 CIRCLE 700, 500, 30

320 REM Draw connecting lines
330 COLOR 7
340 LINE 100, 100 TO 400, 300
350 LINE 700, 100 TO 400, 300
360 LINE 100, 500 TO 400, 300
370 LINE 700, 500 TO 400, 300

380 END
